Class DefaultSRISocketReader

java.lang.Object
  com.sri.common.net.DefaultSRISocketReader
All Implemented Interfaces:
SRISocketReader
Direct Known Subclasses:
CommServer
public class DefaultSRISocketReader
extends java.lang.Object
implements SRISocketReader

This provides a default implementation of the SRISocketReader interface. This allows the implemmenting reader to ommit unused methods, and use default actions for authentication.

Version:
1.5
Author:
Joseph Monti, Smart Robots
